name: Crystallis VoidSlayer (AC)
description: Through Kotaro's research, Crystallis has managed to forge an armor capable of manipulating the properties of void entities within Nulgath's Nation. It is said that the head of Crystallis' division of Void Slayers, Commander Quadryxus donned this armor to equilibrate the outcomes of the Dage versus Nulgath War, which ultimately ensured victory for the Legion.
